            <h2><a href="/news-events/articles/2024/03-march/university-of-macau-open-access/">University of Macau strikes deal to join our growing global Open Access community</a></h2>
<p><em>26 March 2024</em> The addition of Macau to our OA community takes the total number of countries and regions in which we have partner organisations up to 41.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-image-block__img">
            
